            "score": 1,
            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1520975913,
            "creation_date": 1520967369,
            "body": "<p>corrected code with your style shuold be:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>public static int q1(HashMap&lt;String ,String&gt; name) {\n\n    String longest = \"\";\n    //Iterting only though values, not keys\n    for (String key : name.values()) {\n      if(key.length() &gt; longest.length() )\n      {\n      longest = key;\n\n      }\n\n    }\n    //return longest, no need to save in a new string.\n    return longest.length();\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
            "answer_id": 49263871,
            "question_id": 49263227,
            "last_edit_date": 1520975913
        },
        {
